  <title>GIVE HOPE TO THOSE IN NEED</title>
  <link>https://help.unicef.org/zakat2022</link>
  <description>&lt;span&gt;GIVE HOPE TO THOSE IN NEED&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span&gt;&lt;span lang="" about="https://help.unicef.org/user/1461" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" xml:lang=""&gt;asobirjonov&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span&gt;Mon, 02/28/2022 - 16:17&lt;/span&gt;

      &lt;div class="field field--name-field-body-paragraphs field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field--items"&gt;
              &lt;div class="field--item"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-80971 paragraph paragraph--type--html-text paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
            &lt;div class="row"&gt;
                                    
                        &lt;div class="col-12 field field--name-field-html-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;A humanitarian emergency unfolds in Afghanistan&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Around the world, Muslim communities are coming together to commemorate the holy month of Ramadan through prayer and fasting. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But millions of children and families in Afghanistan are unable to have a proper meal to start and break their fast, living through a devastating humanitarian and economic crisis.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are already 1.1 million children in the country suffering from acute malnutrition.  Rising malnutrition, an unprecedented food crisis, drought and disruptions to vital health centers have left more than half of the population in need of assistance. This is a humanitarian emergency and we need to act fast. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is no better time than now. This Ramadan, give your Zakat to help Afghan families who need urgent support UNICEF provides cash assistance to the most vulnerable families, who will use these vital funds to buy food, clothes, medicines or whatever else they need to survive in this time of crisis. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field--item"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-81096 paragraph paragraph--type--donate-button paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
