                        &lt;div class="col-12 field field--name-field-caption field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;“For a poor family like mine, this money will solve thousands of our problems.” Says Mohammad Karim, 65-year-old farmer from Nuristan, an eastern province of Afghanistan.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;He received 17,500 Afghani (approximately US$150) through UNICEF's cash assistance program to support his family.&lt;/p&gt;
