    </item>
<item>
  <title>GIVE HOPE TO THOSE IN NEED</title>
  <link>https://help.unicef.org/zakat2022</link>
  <description>&lt;span&gt;GIVE HOPE TO THOSE IN NEED&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span&gt;&lt;span lang="" about="https://help.unicef.org/user/1461" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" xml:lang=""&gt;asobirjonov&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span&gt;Mon, 02/28/2022 - 16:17&lt;/span&gt;

      &lt;div class="field field--name-field-body-paragraphs field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field--items"&gt;
              &lt;div class="field--item"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-80971 paragraph paragraph--type--html-text paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
            &lt;div class="row"&gt;
                                    
                        &lt;div class="col-12 field field--name-field-html-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;A humanitarian emergency unfolds in Afghanistan&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Around the world, Muslim communities are coming together to commemorate the holy month of Ramadan through prayer and fasting. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But millions of children and families in Afghanistan are unable to have a proper meal to start and break their fast, living through a devastating humanitarian and economic crisis.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are already 1.1 million children in the country suffering from acute malnutrition.  Rising malnutrition, an unprecedented food crisis, drought and disruptions to vital health centers have left more than half of the population in need of assistance. This is a humanitarian emergency and we need to act fast. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is no better time than now. This Ramadan, give your Zakat to help Afghan families who need urgent support UNICEF provides cash assistance to the most vulnerable families, who will use these vital funds to buy food, clothes, medicines or whatever else they need to survive in this time of crisis. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field--item"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-81096 paragraph paragraph--type--donate-button paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
            &lt;div class="row"&gt;
                                    &lt;div class="col-12 text-center field field--name-field-donate-button-text field--type-string field--label-hidden field--items"&gt;
          &lt;a id="donate-btn" class="btn btn-default btn-orange btn-primary" href="#main-content"&gt; This Ramadan help more families like Mohammad Karim’s fight hunger&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

                            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field--item"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-81101 paragraph paragraph--type--html-text paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
            &lt;div class="row"&gt;
                                    
                        &lt;div class="col-12 field field--name-field-background-color field--type-color-field-type field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;div class="hidden"&gt;rgb(28,171,226)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            
                        &lt;div class="col-12 field field--name-field-html-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;h3 class="text-align-center"&gt;&lt;span class="text-white"&gt;Our goal is to reach 80,000 most vulnerable households in four provinces with highest prevalence of poverty in Afghanistan.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;h3 class="text-align-center"&gt;&lt;span class="text-white"&gt;Together, we can make the true meaning of Ramadan shine in homes and hearts throughout Afghanistan during this holy month. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field--item"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-81126 has-media paragraph paragraph--type--image-with-caption paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
            &lt;div class="row"&gt;
                                    
                        &lt;div class="col-12 field field--name-field-image-media field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;div&gt;
  
  
            &lt;div data-blazy="" class="blazy blazy--field blazy--field-media-image blazy--field-media-image---custom field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;




                  &lt;div class="media media--blazy media--bundle--image media--loading is-b-loading media--responsive media--image"&gt;  &lt;picture&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (min-width: 1200px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_desktop/public/2022-02/UN0574454.jpg?itok=MvHtHjVM 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1199px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-02/UN0574454.jpg?itok=nrb7YgQH 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_mobile/public/2022-02/UN0574454.jpg?itok=6D6mc_yI 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;img class="media__image media__element b-lazy b-responsive img-responsive" data-src="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-02/UN0574454.jpg?itok=nrb7YgQH" src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D'http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg'%20viewBox%3D'0%200%202048%201365'%2F%3E" alt="poor-afghanistan" typeof="foaf:Image" /&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
        
  
&lt;/div&gt;
      
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                        &lt;div class="col-12 field field--name-field-caption field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;“For a poor family like mine, this money will solve thousands of our problems.” Says Mohammad Karim, 65-year-old farmer from Nuristan, an eastern province of Afghanistan.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;He received 17,500 Afghani (approximately US$150) through UNICEF's cash assistance program to support his family.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
