  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-geographic-region field--type-entity-reference field--label-above"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field--label"&gt;Geographic region&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field--item"&gt;&lt;a href="https://help.unicef.org/taxonomy/term/811" hreflang="en"&gt;MENA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
</description>
  <pubDate>Mon, 28 Feb 2022 16:17:09 +0000</pubDate>
    <dc:creator>asobirjonov</dc:creator>
    <guid isPermaLink="false">5211 at https://help.unicef.org</guid>
    </item>
<item>
  <title>This Ramadan, make a gift to help deliver therapeutic food to children like Aseel</title>
  <link>https://help.unicef.org/ramadan2022</link>
  <description>&lt;span&gt;This Ramadan, make a gift to help deliver therapeutic food to children like Aseel&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span&gt;&lt;span lang="" about="https://help.unicef.org/user/16" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" xml:lang=""&gt;Jeremy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span&gt;Mon, 02/28/2022 - 16:17&lt;/span&gt;

      &lt;div class="field field--name-field-body-paragraphs field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field--items"&gt;
              &lt;div class="field--item"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-80951 paragraph paragraph--type--html-text paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
            &lt;div class="row"&gt;
                                    
                        &lt;div class="col-12 field field--name-field-html-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Together as a community, we can reach further&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Aseel is 2 years old and he has been suffering with severe acute malnutrition since he was 2 months old. He received treatment in a hospital supported by UNICEF and after 4 months he started to gain weight. But his fight against malnutrition continues, and the experience of seeing their child go hungry still remains in his family’s memory. In countries like Yemen and Afghanistan, the malnutrition rates are soaring, but the support of generous donors can help bring hope.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Around the world, Muslim communities are coming together to commemorate the holy month of Ramadan through prayer and fasting.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But too many children like Aseel and their families are unable to have a proper meal to start and break their fast. This Ramadan, your sadaqah can help UNICEF provide life-saving and critical supplies like therapeutic food, access to water and much more to children in Yemen, Syria, Afghanistan and many other parts of the world.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;UNICEF is the global leader in RUTF procurement, purchasing and distributing across the world this nutrient-rich, peanut-based paste that saves lives. In 2021, with UNICEF support, 3.1 million children in Yemen received micronutrients to help them fight malnutrition.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;We need you to continue this work. &lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Join us to give a better future to the most vulnerable children. There is no better time than now, as we gather and reflect and celebrate one of the most important moments of the year. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field--item"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-80966 paragraph paragraph--type--html-text paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
            &lt;div class="row"&gt;
                                    
                        &lt;div class="col-12 field field--name-field-background-color field--type-color-field-type field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;div class="hidden"&gt;rgb(28,171,226)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            
                        &lt;div class="col-12 field field--name-field-html-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;h3 class="text-align-center"&gt;&lt;span class="text-white"&gt;Donate to UNICEF this Ramadan and help us reach children like Fatima, Gosson and Sajeed. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;h3 class="text-align-center"&gt;&lt;span class="text-white"&gt;There’s no better time than now to save a life.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field--item"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-80711 paragraph paragraph--type--columns paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
                            
            &lt;div class="row justify-content-center field field--name-field-columns field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field--items"&gt;
                            &lt;div style="flex-basis: 33%; align-self: flex-start" class="col col--column"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-80716 paragraph paragraph--type--column paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
                    
                        &lt;div class="column-image column-float-animation field field--name-field-image-media field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;div&gt;
  
  
            &lt;div data-blazy="" class="blazy blazy--field blazy--field-media-image blazy--field-media-image---custom field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;




                  &lt;div class="media media--blazy media--bundle--image media--loading is-b-loading media--responsive media--image"&gt;  &lt;picture&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (min-width: 1200px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_desktop/public/2022-03/UN0536066.jpg?itok=lgCFqPAo 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1199px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-03/UN0536066.jpg?itok=sTDnnyjc 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_mobile/public/2022-03/UN0536066.jpg?itok=d983ASl_ 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;img class="media__image media__element b-lazy b-responsive img-responsive" data-src="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-03/UN0536066.jpg?itok=sTDnnyjc" src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D'http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg'%20viewBox%3D'0%200%20600%20350'%2F%3E" alt="Fatima, child with malnutrition in Yemen" typeof="foaf:Image" /&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
        
  
&lt;/div&gt;
      
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                        &lt;div class="column-body field field--name-field-html-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;As many other children under 5, Fatima arrived in a hospital in Yemen suffering from severe dehydration and malnutrition, resulting in kidney failure. She was put on a treatment programme and is recovering now. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
            &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div style="flex-basis: 33%; align-self: flex-start" class="col col--column"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-80721 paragraph paragraph--type--column paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
                    
                        &lt;div class="column-image column-float-animation field field--name-field-image-media field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;div&gt;
  
  
            &lt;div data-blazy="" class="blazy blazy--field blazy--field-media-image blazy--field-media-image---custom field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;




                  &lt;div class="media media--blazy media--bundle--image media--loading is-b-loading media--responsive media--image"&gt;  &lt;picture&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (min-width: 1200px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_desktop/public/2022-03/UN0492356.jpg?itok=_dg4x8HC 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1199px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-03/UN0492356.jpg?itok=hO1_lbxU 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_mobile/public/2022-03/UN0492356.jpg?itok=qqvz1ztB 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;img class="media__image media__element b-lazy b-responsive img-responsive" data-src="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-03/UN0492356.jpg?itok=hO1_lbxU" src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D'http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg'%20viewBox%3D'0%200%20600%20350'%2F%3E" alt="Gosson, child in Yemen with malnutrition" typeof="foaf:Image" /&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
        
  
&lt;/div&gt;
      
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                        &lt;div class="column-body field field--name-field-html-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;She is one of the many children in Yemen who have been affected by malnutrition. She was referred to a hospital and started a treatment with therapeutic food. Once her health improved, she was back home, where she could finally eat regular food with her mother’s help. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
            &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div style="flex-basis: 33%; align-self: flex-start" class="col col--column"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-80726 paragraph paragraph--type--column paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
                    
                        &lt;div class="column-image column-float-animation field field--name-field-image-media field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;div&gt;
  
  
            &lt;div data-blazy="" class="blazy blazy--field blazy--field-media-image blazy--field-media-image---custom field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;




                  &lt;div class="media media--blazy media--bundle--image media--loading is-b-loading media--responsive media--image"&gt;  &lt;picture&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (min-width: 1200px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_desktop/public/2022-03/UN0574478-%281%29.jpg?itok=Bw-_HGnk 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1199px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-03/UN0574478-%281%29.jpg?itok=h0cDJk0B 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_mobile/public/2022-03/UN0574478-%281%29.jpg?itok=drn92dZ7 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;img class="media__image media__element b-lazy b-responsive img-responsive" data-src="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-03/UN0574478-%281%29.jpg?itok=h0cDJk0B" src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D'http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg'%20viewBox%3D'0%200%20600%20350'%2F%3E" alt="Sajeed, child in Afghanistan" typeof="foaf:Image" /&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
        
  
&lt;/div&gt;
      
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                        &lt;div class="column-body field field--name-field-html-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;In Afghanistan, the situation has become dire for many families in the brink of poverty. Cash assistance is being distributed by UNICEF to help vulnerable families like Sajeed’s. This money will help them meet critical needs like food this Ramadan. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
            &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
    
                    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field--item"&gt;    &lt;div class="paragraph-80731 paragraph paragraph--type--html-text paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
            &lt;div class="row"&gt;
                                    
                        &lt;div class="col-12 field field--name-field-html-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Your sadaqah can make a difference this Ramadan. &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field--item"&gt;  &lt;div class="paragraph-80751 paragraph paragraph--type--cards paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
    &lt;div class="container"&gt;
              
            &lt;div class="row justify-content-center field field--name-field-cards field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field--items"&gt;
                            &lt;div class="col col--card"&gt;&lt;div class="paragraph-80736 card"&gt;

  &lt;div class="card-header"&gt;
    
    
                        &lt;div class="card-title field--item"&gt;Nutrition &lt;/div&gt;
            
  &lt;/div&gt;

  
                        &lt;div class="card-image field--item"&gt;&lt;div&gt;
  
  
            &lt;div data-blazy="" class="blazy blazy--field blazy--field-media-image blazy--field-media-image---custom field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;




                  &lt;div class="media media--blazy media--bundle--image media--loading is-b-loading media--responsive media--image"&gt;  &lt;picture&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (min-width: 1200px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_desktop/public/2022-02/UN0551770.jpg?itok=Lmu1hRIw 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1199px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-02/UN0551770.jpg?itok=C5dj0QNM 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_mobile/public/2022-02/UN0551770.jpg?itok=uVh_Uc_E 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;img class="media__image media__element b-lazy b-responsive img-responsive" data-src="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-02/UN0551770.jpg?itok=C5dj0QNM" src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D'http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg'%20viewBox%3D'0%200%206000%204000'%2F%3E" alt="nutrition" typeof="foaf:Image" /&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
        
  
&lt;/div&gt;
      
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                        &lt;div class="card-body field--item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;PlumpyNut are sackets of therapeutic food used to treat children affected by severe acute malnutrition. Each package contains a peanut-based paste that can help recover a child within weeks. Providing this treatment to children is key to help them recover as quickly as possible.  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class="col col--card"&gt;&lt;div class="paragraph-80741 card"&gt;

  &lt;div class="card-header"&gt;
    
    
                        &lt;div class="card-title field--item"&gt;Water&lt;/div&gt;
            
  &lt;/div&gt;

  
                        &lt;div class="card-image field--item"&gt;&lt;div&gt;
  
  
            &lt;div data-blazy="" class="blazy blazy--field blazy--field-media-image blazy--field-media-image---custom field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;




                  &lt;div class="media media--blazy media--bundle--image media--loading is-b-loading media--responsive media--image"&gt;  &lt;picture&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (min-width: 1200px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_desktop/public/2022-02/UN0536149.jpg?itok=kCUsGkcS 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1199px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-02/UN0536149.jpg?itok=oJPdNFp9 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_mobile/public/2022-02/UN0536149.jpg?itok=jtnQVKOR 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;img class="media__image media__element b-lazy b-responsive img-responsive" data-src="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-02/UN0536149.jpg?itok=oJPdNFp9" src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D'http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg'%20viewBox%3D'0%200%205760%203840'%2F%3E" alt="water" typeof="foaf:Image" /&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
        
  
&lt;/div&gt;
      
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                        &lt;div class="card-body field--item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;In Yemen, your sadaqah can help to provide water and sanitation services to displaced populations and schools. Your support can bring assistance in the form of water points and communal water tanks, latrines, hygiene kits and household water treatment tablets.  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class="col col--card"&gt;&lt;div class="paragraph-80746 card"&gt;

  &lt;div class="card-header"&gt;
    
    
                        &lt;div class="card-title field--item"&gt;Cash Assistance&lt;/div&gt;
            
  &lt;/div&gt;

  
                        &lt;div class="card-image field--item"&gt;&lt;div&gt;
  
  
            &lt;div data-blazy="" class="blazy blazy--field blazy--field-media-image blazy--field-media-image---custom field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;




                  &lt;div class="media media--blazy media--bundle--image media--loading is-b-loading media--responsive media--image"&gt;  &lt;picture&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (min-width: 1200px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_desktop/public/2022-02/UN0574454.jpg?itok=MvHtHjVM 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1199px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-02/UN0574454.jpg?itok=nrb7YgQH 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;source srcset="" media="all and (max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_mobile/public/2022-02/UN0574454.jpg?itok=6D6mc_yI 1x"&gt;&lt;/source&gt;&lt;img class="media__image media__element b-lazy b-responsive img-responsive" data-src="/sites/default/files/styles/responsive_tablet/public/2022-02/UN0574454.jpg?itok=nrb7YgQH" src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D'http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg'%20viewBox%3D'0%200%202048%201365'%2F%3E" alt="poor-afghanistan" typeof="foaf:Image" /&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
        
  
&lt;/div&gt;
      
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
                        &lt;div class="card-body field--item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Helping the most vulnerable families to meet their basic needs is our goal in 4 provinces in Afghanistan. Every month, each household receives a lifeline of $80 to buy food, clothes and medicines for their children. This money is making a difference in their lives, helping them to survive. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
            
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
