                        &lt;div class="col-12 field field--name-field-html-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;h2 class="text-align-center"&gt;&lt;span class="text-white"&gt;Give your sadaqah to children and families in need&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p class="text-align-center"&gt;&lt;span class="text-white"&gt;There is no better time than now. Your generosity will bring hope to Muslims in need in this Ramadan. With UNICEF, your gift will reach them with the therapeutic food, water services and cash assistance that they need to survive and thrive. Show your generosity this Ramadan.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class="text-align-center"&gt;&lt;span class="text-white"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Donate your sadaqah. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
